This paper is likely to belong to the category of "Computation and Language" (cs.CL) as it deals with the emergence of language in artificial agents. It also involves machine learning techniques, which makes it relevant to the categories of "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI) and "Learning" (cs.LG). The paper also explores the impact of environmental pressures on language structure, which could be relevant to the category of "Systems and Control" (cs.SD) as well as "Neural and Evolutionary Computing" (cs.NE).
